4:
So uh... Sohvi, what's this important
announcement you want to share?
18:
I popped out a little pip-squeak of
my own.
26:
I'm telling you right now, there's no
way it's mine!
29:
She must be having delusions since
we ran into that lost kid a few days
back—
44:
...Sohvi, you should turn yourself in
before it's too late.
49:
Wait, I think I know what this is... It's
one of her plushie things!
53:
Ding-ding! That's right! He's made
from Nimbus's fur and one of my
concoctions!
67: How can you be so calm about this?!
71:
Because this is the second time
she's pulled this crap on us.
79:
...You're kidding. This IS only the
second time, right?
83:
A-anyway, Sohvi, I think you're really
crossing the line here!
85:
Shywe's going to be really mad that
you're using the sprites for
something like this...
90:
Oh, Alk, you worrywart! The sprites
have nothing to do with this at all!
99:
I used some Devourer of Stars
material I stole from a certain
research lab!
103:
This is even WORSE than I could've
imagined!
110:
I did NOT sign up to be part of a
horror movie today!
113:
Hehee, he's a feisty one, isn't he?
Soon he'll be hitting his rebellious
years!
118:
That THING ain't no KID, you hear
me?!
123:
What do we do? If other people
catch wind of this, we're gonna have
a situation on our hands.
126:
We gotta put it out of its misery
before anything else happens!
131:
H-how can you say that, Nimbus?
He's a symbol of our love!
134:
In what world does a symbol of love
sprout TENTACLES?!
143:
I must've miscalculated the
adhesives needed... Mama's so sorry!
146:
But one day... We'll meet again, I
know it!
150: I can't do this anymore... I can't...
153: It's time I put an end to this!
162:
Listen up, Sohvi. I'm making you my
girl.
168:
W-wait, for real?! Marry me,
Nimby-Wimby! We can have the
ceremony right now! I've got a dress
and tux ready—
175:
I'm not your man. I'm making you
my girl.
177:
You don't do anything without my
permission, got it?
181:
Nimbus, what's with the sleazy guy
act?
186:
Well, what else am I supposed to
do? She's gonna keep running wild
otherwise!
211:
Are you certain this is the best way?
I can't commend this kind of
behavior...
215:
H-hey, as long as they're fine with it,
then... it's fine, right?
218:
Ehehe! I can finally be as
lovey-dovey as I want with my
Nimby-Wimby!
222:
No, you can't! Absolutely no clinging
allowed! That's an order!
227:
You don't have to act all shy,
Nimby-Wimby. I know exactly what
you REALLY feel inside!
235:
She doesn't listen to a single word
anyone says, no matter what they're
saying!
240:
Aaaahhh! I take back everything I
said earlier! Let go of me! Get
awaaay!
245:
I love you, Nimby-Wimby! Ehehe!
Ehehehehe!
